<h1>Reset Your Password</h1>

<p>
  We received a request to reset your password for your MOSSLET account. No worries – it happens to the best of us!
</p>

<p>
  To create a new password and regain access to your private social space, click the button below:
</p>

<EmailComponents.button_centered to={@url} color="blue" size="lg">
  Reset Your Password
</EmailComponents.button_centered>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.status type="warning">
  <strong>⚠️ Security Note:</strong>
  This password reset link will expire in 2 hours for your protection.
</EmailComponents.status>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<p>Once you reset your password, you'll be back to enjoying:</p>
<ul>
  <li>🔒 Your private timeline with no algorithms</li>
  <li>💬 Secure, encrypted messaging</li>
  <li>🌱 A calm, peaceful social media experience</li>
</ul>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.top_border>
  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    If you're having trouble clicking the button, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:
    <a href={@url}>{@url}</a>
  </EmailComponents.small_text>

  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your account remains secure.
  </EmailComponents.small_text>
</EmailComponents.top_border>
